<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.everlore.com/MB_SHOW.asp?SID=7&SN=EverQuest&TID=1093896&TN=Velious+Faction&FID=67&FN=Paladin&SURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Eeverlore%2Ecom&CAT=Classes&PL=3">www.everlore.com/MB_SHOW....asses&PL=3</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
